Class LifeSupportUpdateVisitor

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.components.visitors.LifeSupportUpdateVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
ComponentVisitor
public class LifeSupportUpdateVisitor extends Object implements ComponentVisitor
Visitor used to check whether or not a CabinComponent's crew dies after a AlienLifeSupportComponent is destroyed.
